snippet.title: Moonstone Island - Meet the Spirits!
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1658150/Moonstone_Island/

Meet the Nature Spirits of Moonstone Island! Battle, Tame, and Befriend up to 100 spirits that will keep you company during your Alchemist training. How many spirits will you encounter during your year away from home?

Moonstone Island is coming to PC and Nintendo Switch in 2023!
